Information We Collect: Name, email, password (for authentication), performance schedules.
How We Use It: To authenticate users, manage performers and schedules, and provide app functionality.
Data Sharing: We do not share personal information with third parties except to the theatre for performance management.
Security: We store your data securely with Firebase.
User Rights: You can request access or deletion of your data by contacting us at info@unioncomedy.com.
